### ── LOCAL TESTING (Docker running on your machine) ──────────

### 1. Health check — is the app running?
GET http://localhost:7860/

###

### 2. First question (no history)
POST http://localhost:7860/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "What is the story about?",
  "history": []
}

###

### 3. Follow-up question (with history)
POST http://localhost:7860/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "What does the villain do?",
  "history": [
    {"role": "user",      "content": "What is the story about?"},
    {"role": "assistant", "content": "The story is about Snow White..."}
  ]
}

###

### 4. Character question
POST http://localhost:7860/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "Who are the main characters?",
  "history": []
}

###

### 5. End of story
POST http://localhost:7860/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "What happens at the end of the story?",
  "history": []
}


### ── HUGGING FACE TESTING (after cloud deployment) ───────────
### Replace YOUR_HF_USERNAME with your actual Hugging Face username

### 6. Health check — HF
GET https://YOUR_HF_USERNAME-my-rag-app.hf.space/

###

### 7. Ask a question — HF
POST https://YOUR_HF_USERNAME-my-rag-app.hf.space/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "What is the story about?",
  "history": []
}
